[以色列國軍](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaza_flotilla_raid
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaza_flotilla_raid")先前攻擊前往加薩走廊的船隊[Mavi
Marmara](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MV_Mavi_Marmara
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MV_Mavi_Marmara")，造成九人死亡、多人受傷，讓全球許多人發聲支持加薩走廊民眾，包括[土耳其](http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-
defense/turkey-recalls-envoy-over-gaza-flotilla-deaths-accuses-israel-of-
state-terrorism-1.293186 "http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-
defense/turkey-recalls-envoy-over-gaza-flotilla-deaths-accuses-israel-of-
state-
terrorism-1.293186")、[厄瓜多](http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3898523,00.html
"http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3898523,00.html")、[南非](http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5ioi_0jtO9RjMwPNRoXNCndRPRq3gD9G3PN403
"http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5ioi_0jtO9RjMwPNRoXNCndRPRq3gD9G3PN403")等國均召回駐以色列大使，[其他國家](http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704490204575279222111875404.html?mod=googlenews_wsj
"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704490204575279222111875404.html?mod=googlenews_wsj")則要求由中立單位進行調查；[尼加拉瓜](http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3898523,00.html
"http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3898523,00.html")更進一步，直接與以色列斷交。

與此同時，全球各地都出現遊行活動，從瑞典斯德哥爾摩到巴西聖保羅，社運份子與關心民眾都走上街頭，抗議暴力與以色列持續封鎖加薩走廊。

鄰國黎巴嫩[抗爭群眾](http://thisisbeirut.wordpress.com/2010/06/02/gaza-flotilla-
protest-in-downtown-beirut/
"http://thisisbeirut.wordpress.com/2010/06/02/gaza-flotilla-protest-in-
downtown-beirut/")拿著土耳其國旗，支持來自土耳其的Mavi Marmara船隊。

